---
import SiteLayout from "../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
const stages = ["research", "plan", "benchmark", "run", "analysis", "draft", "review", "submission"];
---

<SiteLayout
  title="How It Works · Argus"
  description="Argus 如何用 LifeSupervisor、四个角色和 SkillLoop 持续经营一个研究项目。"
>
  <section class="page-hero compact">
    <div class="shell">
      <p class="eyebrow">How it works</p>
      <h1>一个项目，两层循环，四个角色。</h1>
      <p class="lede">外层维持项目生命，内层完成一个 mission；状态、失败和下一步不会随对话消失。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section tight">
    <div class="shell architecture">
      <div class="section-head">
        <p class="eyebrow">Architecture</p>
        <h2>LifeSupervisor 让研究持续，SkillLoop 让每轮闭环。</h2>
        <p>
          backlog 空时 Planner 继续排活；Engineer 真正执行；Reviewer 根据 evidence 决定 done、continue 或 blocked。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="role-list">
        <article class="role"><i>M</i><div><h3>Manager</h3><p>入口、vertical 与 stage 权威。</p></div></article>
        <article class="role"><i>P</i><div><h3>Planner</h3><p>提出下一批值得做的工作。</p></div></article>
        <article class="role"><i>E</i><div><h3>Engineer</h3><p>写代码、跑实验、产出 artifact。</p></div></article>
        <article class="role"><i>R</i><div><h3>Reviewer</h3><p>验收、返工、记录 checkpoint。</p></div></article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section surface">
    <div class="shell">
      <div class="section-head">
        <p class="eyebrow">Paper pipeline</p>
        <h2>从一个目标到一篇 PDF。</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="pipeline">
        {stages.map((stage, index) => (
          <div><span>{String(index + 1).padStart(2, "0")}</span><strong>{stage}</strong></div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="shell">
      <div class="section-head">
        <p class="eyebrow">A real run</p>
        <h2>B200 上的 426 次自治搜索。</h2>
        <p>每个点是一轮真实尝试，floor 从 1.0587 推到 0.9636。</p>
      </div>
      <figure class="figure">
        <img src="/assets/nanochat-b200-trajectory.svg" alt="B200 nanochat 进化曲线" />
        <figcaption>val BPB 越低越好；Argus 最终超过 human SOTA 0.9646。</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
